<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-78-0239 </DOCNO><TEXT>This 10-chapter book is intended as a student text and as a source book.It covers nucleonics, radioactivity, interaction of radiation with matter,nuclear radiation, nuclear reactions, interactions between the nucleusand the electrons, nuclear transformations, radioactive elements, nuclearenergy, and radionuclides. This English edition is translated from theoriginal German edition, Radiochemie, published in 1981 by Verlag MaritzDiesterweg GmbH and Company. Chapter exercises, solutions, a bibliography,and an index are included.</TEXT></DOC>